(-1580099,'Mortal heroes, your victory here today was foretold long ago. My brother''s anguished cry of defeat will echo across the universe, bringing renewed hope to all those who still stand against the Burning Crusade.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 12515, 0, 0, 0,'prophet velen - SAY1'),
